item.title: CVE-2024-32145|2024-04-15T07:03:13.896Z -- PineWise -- WP Google Analytics Events
item.description: Improper Neutralization of Input During Web Page Generation ('Cross-site Scripting') vulnerability in PineWise WP Google Analytics Events allows Reflected XSS.This issue affects WP Google Analytics Events: from n/a through 2.8.0.
